Bryan Cogman, the writer of “Game of Thrones” has released 21 must watch episodes to see ahead of the final season set to be aired on Sunday, April 14th. The list is meant to serve as a refresher for both old and new “Game of Thrones” fans to get them ready for the final six episodes. Find below the 21 episodes named by Cogman as a must-see before jumping into Season 8. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-898466 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="718" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter.jpg 1200w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-640x359.jpg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-1062x596.jpg 1062w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-320x179.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-281x158.jpg 281w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-562x316.jpg 562w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-531x299.jpg 531w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-487x273.jpg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-974x546.jpg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/A-scene-from-Game-of-Thrones-Photo-Twitter-600x337.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Which episodes are your favourites that you think should have made C0ogman’s must-see episodes?